#: build/C/man2/modify_ldt.2:190
msgid ""
"The normal use for B<modify_ldt>()  is to run legacy 16-bit or segmented 32-"
"bit code.  Not all kernels allow 16-bit segments to be installed, however."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: build/C/man2/modify_ldt.2:198
msgid ""
